data.description: Incredible location – 2 blocks from Minnehaha Creek on generous corner lot!  34 x 40 Kitchen and Family Room addition in 2001.  One level living - Main Level Primary Suite with private bath and jetted tub. Center island Kitchen opens to Main Level Family Room with gas fireplace. Beautiful Dining Room with tray ceiling and inset lighting. Laundry and additional ¾ Bath on Main Level, as well as a sun filled Living Room/Office/Media Room. Two additional Bedrooms and ¾ Bath in Lower Level, along with expansive crawl space storage.  Spacious 2 car insulated garage with overhead storage.  Incredible opportunity in highly coveted Armatage neighborhood.
